Doxygen documentation

Generate the HTML documentation by running from this folder:

    doxygen Doxyfile

Output is written to doxygen/html/. Open doxygen/html/index.html in a browser.

Configuration:
- Input:   ../src  (recursive, external/ excluded)
- Output:  html/
- Graphs:  call graphs and caller graphs enabled (requires graphviz)

UML collaboration diagrams for the main classes are in the uml/ subfolder.

